Put the pan into the refrigerator and close it, after few minutes take it out and close it.
Turn left and walk a few steps
Put the pan on the countertop.

Pick up the pan from the couch.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on the right.
Put the pan in the bottom shelf of the fridge to cool down and take it out.
Turn left to face the countertop cabinet.
Put the pan on the countertop next to the microwave.

Pick up the pan from the sofa.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Cool the pan in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to reach the counter top.
Put the pan on the counter top.
